query:
SELECT 
  (SELECT COUNT(*) FROM consultasPrenatal WHERE gestanteId = 10) as total_consultas,
  (SELECT COUNT(*) FROM resultadosExames WHERE gestanteId = 10) as total_exames,
  (SELECT COUNT(*) FROM ultrassons WHERE gestanteId = 10) as total_ultrassons,
  (SELECT dum FROM gestantes WHERE id = 10) as dum_atualizada;
